Architecture Deep-Dive

Control Plane (Master Node) Components:

API Server: Central communication hub; all requests go through it
ETCD: Key-value database storing cluster state and configuration
Scheduler: Finds best placement for pods across nodes
Controller Manager: Maintains desired cluster state (e.g., replica counts)
Worker Node Components:

Kubelet: Agent that communicates with master and executes pod tasks
Kube-proxy: Handles service networking and internet exposure
Container Runtime: Docker engine that runs containers
